|6 |      │ │ └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (BC2HOST)|:EX10000|
|7 |      │ │   └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR         |        |
|8 |      │ │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN         |T1      |
|9 |      │ └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR             |        |
